Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.96,0:00:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《断头谷》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Previously on Sleepy Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮弗・米尔斯  你以前帮过你姐姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Jennifer Mills, you've helped your sister before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.83,0:00:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比说这件事你能帮上忙  所以她让我找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Abbie wants me to bring you into this, says you'll be valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我需要知道  \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}But I need to know-- 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是帮我们还是不帮  -帮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- are you in or out? - In.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坠入爱河  然后结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}You fell in love, you get married,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却完全不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}but the whole time you have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.35,0:00:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的妻子是个女巫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}that your wife is a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎么会不知道呢  -她在保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- How could you not know? - She was protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是古老骑士修道会的一员  立誓对抗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}We are part of an ancient order sworn to fight the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断头谷中的黑暗势力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}that hides in Sleepy Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面对的是我们远不能控制的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}We're dealing with forces so beyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远远不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Beyond beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Jenny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是关键  中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}That's the key, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我们更加\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Now, more than ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要卡特里娜了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}we need Katrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么不敢说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}What is it you're afraid to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我为什么会在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I believe I know why I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-为什么  -伊卡伯德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- Why? - Ichabod!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的车正缓缓驶近那儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I'm pulling up to it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.48,0:00:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  我会给你发照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Yes, I'll send you pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.08,0:00:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直不敢相信它曾属于我的家族\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I can't believe it used to belong to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  我就是很好奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I know. I'm just so curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尽我所能了解这里的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I want to learn everything I can about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是附近最古老的一座宅院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's one of the oldest homes in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花了五年才把地契搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It took me five years to secure the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.03,0:01:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让它恢复旧时的光辉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Oh, I'd like to restore it to its original grandeur.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有好多工作要完成\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}We have a lot of work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.13,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.45,0:01:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是历史  山姆  准确地说是我家族的历史\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's history, Sam-- my family's history, to be exact--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以放尊重点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}so show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生在这里的事应该被铭记\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Things happened here that need to be remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.50,0:01:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着像鬼屋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Looks haunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为保镖而言  你算够胆小的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}For a bodyguard, you are a very fearful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜  莉娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Lena. Lena!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在知道这房子结构没问题前  你不能...\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Until we know it's structurally safe in there, you are not go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该把一切都恢复原样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}We should restore all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些顽固的破树枝\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Stubborn little brutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆  我们应该带把修枝剪来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Sam! We should've brought the hedge clippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地方完完全全地...\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}The place is completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想指出一日三餐的传统已经消失殆尽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I'm merely noting the eradication of a thrice-daily tradition,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再没人好好腾出时间来吃顿饭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}wherein each meal is treated with the proper allowance of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是说驾车外带就没给我留下深刻印象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Not that the "Drive-through" wasn't impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.35,0:02:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且虽然餐馆起了那个名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}And despite this establishment's nomenclature,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可跟我吃过的苏格兰菜不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}this resembles no Scottish meal I've ever eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说这些  是来自奥地利统治期的荷兰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}These are from the Austrian Netherlands, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还做得很糟糕\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}And dreadfully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的感恩节估计就这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}This is probably as much of a Thanksgiving as we're getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}What about your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是家庭团聚时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}This is "Family time."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说自打她从精神病院出院就由我当监护人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I don't think my having conservatorship over her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我不觉得这就意味着接下来会演变成\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}since her release from the nuthouse necessarily leads
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在餐桌上互递红莓酱的温情场面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}to "Pass the cranberry sauce."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,递什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鸡  红莓酱  南瓜馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Turkey, cranberry sauce, pumpkin pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8} 指1620年搭乘五月花号移居美国的英国清教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是清教徒吃的那些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}You know, all the stuff the Pilgrims ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些清教徒连做酱的糖都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}The Pilgrims didn't have any sugar to make a sauce,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更别说馅饼了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}let alone a pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且吃的是鹿肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}And venison,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是火鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}not turkey, was served.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕能有只饿得半死的野鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It would've been a miracle for a single half-starved
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在寒冬里出现就是奇迹  -等下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- pheasant to trot past during such a harsh winter... - Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Pheasants?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提到节日\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}All this talk of holidays,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火鸡和家庭时光\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}turkeys, family time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我平添烦恼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}irks me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为卡特里娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Because of Katrina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不能和妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}If I can't be with my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共度感恩庆祝之时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}during a time of thanks and celebration,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要有这么多事物又在不断提醒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}why must there be so many constant reminders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个我无法逃避的现实...\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}of the inescapable fact that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得孤独\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}You're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无意不敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I mean no disrespect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你陪伴对我来说意义重大\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Your company holds the greatest value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.86,0:04:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Crane...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有权恼怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}you have a right to be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你比任何人失去的都多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}You've lost more than anyone ever should.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.01,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  若不能发泄烦恼还要节假日干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Besides, what are holidays for if not airing our grievances?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼过后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}After our nuptials,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对我们将共度的人生充满希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I had such hope for the life Katrina and I were to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去这几周过得太疯狂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's been a crazy few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一晚就会好很多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}You'll feel better after a night off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰  米尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Crane, Mills--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有东西给你们看\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}got something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是哪晚能休息告诉我一声\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Kindly inform me when that night arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息时间到此结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}So much for the proper allowance of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜・吉尔伯特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Lena Gilbert--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慈善家  作家  社会名媛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}philanthropist, author, socialite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尔伯特小姐的血统能追溯到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Miss Gilbert's lineage goes back generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国父那一代\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}to the Founding Fathers.
