Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拉克兰・弗雷德里克斯的名字命名\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Named for Lachlan Fredericks,
