Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陆会议的创始人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}of the Continental Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.92,0:07:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问  他是个狂热的战争支持者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Needless to say, a keen supporter of the war effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他是你的朋友对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}And, I assume, a friend of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道吉尔伯特小姐去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I know where Miss Gilbert went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在市政厅查了这块地的地契\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I pulled the land title and deed from city hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块地属于几个不同的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}This place has had a few different owners,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但自拉克兰・弗雷德里克斯以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}but no one's actually lived here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少有人在这长期居住\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}for more than a few weeks since Lachlan Fredericks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车里没人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许在屋里呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Inside, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你想来的弗雷德里克斯庄园  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Fredericks Manor-- this is where you wanted to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It is indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这完全根本不像我和卡特里娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}But it hardly resembles the residence
