Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也有空  就跟着一起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Finally, my schedule allowed me to accept an invitation.
