Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到弗雷德里克斯庄园  我帮您拿外套\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Welcome to Fredericks Manor. May I take your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谢谢  -这个庄园是拉克兰・弗雷德里克斯的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- Thank you. - The manor belonged to Lachlan Fredericks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道他是个狂热的战争支持者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I knew of him as a dedicated supporter of the war,
