Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他的事情我就不知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}but I had no knowledge of his other causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  亲爱的  你看到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Look around, my love. What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是自由身\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}They're all free.
