Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个庄园就是他们的天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}This estate is a safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个大家寻求避难的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}A place for anyone seeking refuge.
