Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在可是在一间闹鬼的房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}But we're in a damn haunted house.
