Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确保她的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}and ensure her safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  好计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Right. Good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女中尉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你看到她了吗  -看到谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- Did you see her? - Who?
