Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-她刚刚就在我们面前  -什么女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- She was right in front of us. - What woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们面对过女巫\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}We've faced witches,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神的无头骑士\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}a headless rider of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵我们梦境的睡魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}a demon who invades our dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我们也能勇敢的面对这次危机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I'm sure we can brave this little crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说  鬼屋什么的向来吓不倒我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I am saying haunted houses do not work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是小时候  现在亦或是以后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Not as a child, not now, not ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的准则\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}There's a line.
