Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有本一模一样的书\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}She owned a copy identical to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那是什么  -是封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- What is it? - It's a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书竟然保持了多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It survived all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡特里娜的收信地址\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Addressed to Katrina?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我写给她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}One I wrote to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我面对无头骑士的那天早上\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}The morning I faced the Horseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.14,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挚爱的卡特里娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}"My beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你收到封信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}If this missive reaches you,
