Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你下葬几天后  她肯定回来过这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}She must have returned here while you were buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的信放在她最爱的书里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}And leave my letter in her favorite book?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是为了让我找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}It's as though I was meant to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不明白  -我也不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- I don't understand. - Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事不太对劲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}Something's not right about it.
