Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里以前不是这样的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}So it wasn't like this before,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼影重重  乌鸦哀鸣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}all haunted and with crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战争激烈时期  这里曾是希望之地\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}at the height of the war, this was a place of hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是善良之所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}a force for good.
