Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对抗帮助骑士逃脱的恶魔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}that were trying to bust out the Horseman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场面太混乱了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}There was a lot of confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得这些枪都是从哪来的了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}I lost track of what gun belongs to where.
