Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我现在不是来了吗  -其它的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}- I'm here now, aren't I? - The rest?
