Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了感谢艾比重新接受我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}to say thank you to Abbie for taking me in,
