Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这就是一次普通形式的晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&}So this is a normal dinner type thing.
